│                      │  🟢 Opened Chapters (tab bar) 5% │            │
│  🔴 Entities List    ├──────────────────────────────────┤  🩵        │
│        10%           │                                  │  Chapter   │
│                      │   ⬜ MAIN WRITING FIELD  50%     │   List     │
│                      │                                  │   10%      │
│                      │                                  │ (full ht)  │
├──────────────────────┼──────────────────────┬───────────┤            │
│  🟡 Entities Filter  │  🔵 Dynamic Panel   │  🟣       │            │
│        5%            │        10%           │  Entity   │            │
│                      │                      │  Details  │            │
│                      │                      │   15%     │            │
└──────────────────────┴──────────────────────┴───────────┴────────────┘
 ── Status bar — scene recording · dialogue capture · word count ────────
```

**Screen real estate:**

| Zone | % of screen |
|---|---|
| ⬜ Main Writing Field | 50% |
| 🟣 Entity Details | 15% |
| 🩵 Chapter List | 10% |
| 🔴 Entities List | 10% |
| 🔵 Dynamic Panel | 10% |
| 🟡 Entities Filter | 5% |
| 🟢 Chapter Tab Bar | 5% |
| **Total** | **100%** |

**Column widths:** Left (Entities List + Filter) = 10% · Center (Writing + Dynamic + Details) = 80% · Right (Chapter List) = 10%

**Zone behaviours:**

**🔴 Entities List** — scrollable list of entities for the type selected in the filter below. Tap an entity to load it into Entity Details.

**🟡 Entities Filter** — horizontally scrollable row of entity type buttons (Chr, Loc, Fac, Her…). Selecting one reloads the Entities List above.

**🟢 Chapter Tab Bar** — open chapters as closeable tabs. Active chapter highlighted with accent colour underline.

**⬜ Main Writing Field** — the writing canvas. Always visible. Never replaced. Full TextEditor with live word count.

**🔵 Dynamic Panel** — dual purpose. Default (idle): quick notes scratchpad. Active with `⌘⌥[`: Subject Lock search panel. Active with `⌘⌥D`: Define Relationship interface. Operations stack — completing one returns to the previous state.

**🟣 Entity Details** — name, type badge, chapter mention count, and notes for the selected entity. Loads when an entity is tapped in the Entities List, or when Subject Lock activates.

**🩵 Chapter List** — full-height chapter outline for the current book. `+` creates new chapters. Clicking opens a chapter in a tab.

**Status bar** — always-visible strip at the very bottom: scene recording state · dialogue capture state · total word count · current chapter word count.

